The paper discusses achieving secure communications in networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the transmission of messages, which is a topic that falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses multicast channels and neighbor network channels, which are topics that fall under the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), networked systems (cs.NI), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
